---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="A little about Marihella — who I am, what I love, and why this site exists.">
  <div class="about-page">

    <header class="page-header">
      <h1>About Me</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="about-content">

      <section class="about-section">
        <p>
          Hi, I'm Marihella. This is my small corner of the internet where I keep track of
          the things that make life feel a little more magical — whether that is escaping into a new book world, 
          watching and documenting my garden grow, or finding recipes I'll keep coming back to. I made this site just to get some of my thoughts and inspiration out of my brain and onto a page. Let the adventures begin!
          
          
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h3 class="section-title">Things I Love</h3>
        <ul class="loves-list">
          <li>Fantasy novels with fae courts and morally complex characters</li>
          <li>Mountains and forests — especially when they feel otherworldly</li>
          <li>The smell of old bookshops</li>
          <li>Mythical creatures in every form</li>
          <li>A good slow burn</li>
          <li>Fresh rosemary from the garden</li>
          <li>Art that looks like a fairy tale — Abigail Larson, Gretel Lusky, Kay Nielsen</li>
          <li>Rain on windows when you have nowhere to be</li>
          <li>Urban fantasy that makes your city feel strange and alive</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h3 class="section-title">Currently</h3>
        <div class="currently-grid">
          <div class="currently-item">
            <h5>Reading</h5>
            <p>A Court of Thorns and Roses series, Red Rising</p>
          </div>
          <div class="currently-item">
            <h5>Growing</h5>
            <p>A monstera that's getting ideas above its station</p>
          </div>
          <div class="currently-item">
            <h5>Dreaming Of</h5>
            <p>Somewhere with mountains, mist, and a cafe with a fireplace</p>
          </div>
          <div class="currently-item">
            <h5>Baking</h5>
            <p>Rosemary focaccia, always</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h3 class="section-title">Why This Site</h3>
        <p>
          I believe the internet is better when it has weird little personal corners.
          This is mine. It's not optimised, it's not monetised, it doesn't have a newsletter signup.
          It's just a place where I put the things I want to remember.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you've stumbled here somehow — welcome. Pull up a chair. Stay as long as you like.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding: var(--space-4) 0;
  }

  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }
  .page-header h1 { color: var(--color-sage-dark); }

  .about-content {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .loves-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .loves-list li {
    padding: var(--space-2) 0;
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
    position: relative;
    border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--color-gold-light);
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
  }
  .loves-list li::before {
    content: '✦';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
  }

  .currently-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .currently-item {
    background: var(--color-cream);
    border: var(--border-thin);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--space-4);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .currently-item h5 {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
  .currently-item p {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    max-width: none;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
